By: Representatives Lumsden of the 12th, Dempsey of the 13th, and Barton of the 5th
A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending the 2025 Awards of Honor recipient, Virginia Barrow
2 Harman; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Virginia Barrow Harman is a Senior Partner at McRae, Smith, Peek, Harman
4 & Monroe LLP; and
5 WHEREAS, Virginia cares deeply about access to justice for all of the communities of Rome
6 and Floyd County and the environment in which they live; and
7 WHEREAS, she has handled countless pro bono matters, particularly as they relate to the
8 cleanliness of rivers; and
9 WHEREAS, Virginia has served the community through her volunteerism with multiple
10 organizations, serving as Chair of the Board of the local chapter of the American Red Cross,
11 the Capital Fund Raising Committee for the Salvation Army local facility expansion, Planned
12 Giving Committee for the Floyd Healthcare Foundation, Board of Harbor House, Co-host
13 for the annual Pig and Paddle event, the Georgia and Rome Bar Association, the State Bar
14 of Georgia's Disciplinary Board's Review and Investigatory Panels, the Committee on
15 Lawyer Assistance Program for attorneys facing mental health crises and/or substance abuse
